Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:35.26,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Girls' Last Tour
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.97,0:00:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird machinery aside, this place is pretty clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's been closed up this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.77,0:00:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we might be able to find out more\Nabout the past in a place like this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.98,0:00:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff from the past... like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how people in the past lived their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or what they wore, or how they spoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you wanna know that stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.92,0:01:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh hey, the cut's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it goes off sometimes, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's eating some more bullets or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.02,0:01:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.39,0:01:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes we run into someone\Nand become a group of three, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean like Ishii and Kanazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with the cut, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking it feels a little different than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.28,0:01:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, lively, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lonely with it being just us?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...do you feel lonely, Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I guess a little, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh, the stuff inside feels just like... could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.21,0:01:59.68,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Non-Perishable Chocolate\NHigh Calorie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:01:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.88,0:02:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sniff sniff...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a familiar smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to eat? It's kinda dark-colored...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Edible things...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...can be eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.29,0:02:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.09,0:02:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This tastes like that one thing.\NThe chocolate flavor. It's so sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.84,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure do have a good memory\Nwhen it comes to food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, it's gotta be chocolate-flavored something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...yeah, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:58.36,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Non-Perishable Chocolate\NHigh Calorie
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But in a way, that's also\N"something from the past", I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Flavors are information, in a way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Though you can't write them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Say chee...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.59,Typeset,,0,0,0,,CONNECTING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.63,0:03:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some words came up on the camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It can connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, cut...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:35.52,Typeset,,0,0,0,,CONNECTING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:37.23,Typeset,,0,0,0,,SYNCING
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi, those are the pictures we took!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.74,0:03:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's displaying the pictures that were inside the camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.12,0:03:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe they could do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look, man, that takes me back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that far away that you'd be taken back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What're these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,These pictures...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Those aren't ones that we took.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the map guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.36,0:04:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...and who's that girl next to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess Kanazawa took these pictures over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He was alone when we met him...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There are lots of folders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Folders?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.68,0:04:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can open all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! There are so many people...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,These... were all inside the camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.28,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.92,0:05:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhh, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It moved! And talked!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A-are these what they called "videos"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the 12th Report of the\NMachine Evolution Research Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...is it recording?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going, it's going!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm, today's sample is this small machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We have named it No. 17 2nd-Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.90,0:05:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This machine can inject certain programs\Ninto manufacturing equipment,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,forcing the equipment to produce more of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:06:00.62,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They looks like they're around our age...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,One would scarcely consider that this difficult process\Nwould be born from variation and selection…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.54,Default2,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's totally okay to call that evolution!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Saying it's a human design is way too self-serving!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's kinda important!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I've started to get why you\Nwanna know more about the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been just the two of us for a long time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you find out that people used to live like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Midori, it's your Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.35,0:06:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She says she doesn't like you, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell is wrong with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you speak to me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mere, Bochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan formally declared war on\Nthe neighboring states...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we'll put out another report\Nonce we reconcile our opinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Large-scale air raids...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, it's all your fault, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our military has secured a great victory,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.71,0:08:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with the neighboring state's casualties\Nnumbering over fifty million...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we bought French fries!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure love to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning: Electromagnetic bombs\Nhave been deployed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All electronic devices have lost functionality...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Miki comes in first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:43.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,The Bunny and\Nthe Bear's Adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.37,0:08:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birth...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.05,0:08:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All telecommunications between every city\Nand every layer have been lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Father in heaven, we pray you share endless joy\Nwith the brethren you have called to your side...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda feel a little less lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.23,0:09:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably the only one who'll be able to\Nget out through the pipe storehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.80,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you should be able to live\Na long time with just a little food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Grandpa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.58,0:10:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The cut's gone again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what kind of being that thing is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It can open doors, and use machines, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And it uses the receiver to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where were...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.19,0:10:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you bigger than before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Big...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, cut?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I've gotta go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.45,0:11:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna eat me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't talk without that receiver...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just talk to that big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.52,0:12:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you ask it to spit out Yuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be little, but you might actually be\None of mankind's enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,An enemy, so what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I lost Yuu, I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.34,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Chi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.28,0:14:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?! You got eaten, but you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, once I tried, I got out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by tried...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not eat living humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not possess vocal organs,\Nbut we can decipher sound waves as language.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why we have used the equipment on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Juveniles are only capable of short-range\Ntransmission, so these situations sometimes occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This song...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a part of our transmission signal\Nthat the device received.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.55,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what are you guys, and why did you eat Yuu?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We only ingested the small device\Nthat human possessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Even some small devices from the generations of old\Npossess high amounts of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We ingest thermally unstable materials
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and dismantle them internally\Ninto a stable, static state.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,When this processing is complete,\Nthe long period of life activity on Earth will end,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.94,0:16:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Earth will slumber once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.86,0:16:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,When that time comes, we will hibernate as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of our activities in this city have come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All the weapons in the city...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.75,0:17:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The city will slowly come to an eventual halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.83,0:17:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A halt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have surveyed most locations,\Naside from those on the highest level,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and to our knowledge, you are\Nthe only two humans still alive today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.06,0:17:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for bringing this little one to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.32,0:17:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We must move together as a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why're you scared, cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be fine. You've got lots of friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Chi. It said the world's gonna end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.68,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if the world ends... I wouldn't really care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I have you, Yuu, I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So that singing voice was theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.48,0:19:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they got along with the feeling of hopelessness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they seem sad. It's a song about the End.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:08.56,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready, up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.07,0:20:41.96,Typeset,,0,0,0,,Canned Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good thing there were canned goods\Nin the cafeteria, huh, Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.12,0:20:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We're back to being just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,For now... and forever more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lonely with it just being us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're lonely, right, Chi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha-?! I thought you were lonely, Yuu, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.38,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, c'mon! You really aren't honest about how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I-!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. Let's go. Hurry up and get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.99,0:21:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,To the highest level, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. There might be something up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.00,0:21:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There might be nothing up there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a level up there, so we're gonna go up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you going on about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. Which way should we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.39,0:21:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.73,0:21:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.40,0:21:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the wind blows...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.62,0:21:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I guess that's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, Chi, once we get to the top level,\Nlet's go to the Moon next!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who said you wanted to go there, Chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.26,0:22:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.14,0:22:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Moon, huh? Could be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.97,0:22:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
